              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Each sample (10-90 ug/cm2, 25 mm in diam.)",
                " electroplated on a Pt plate (0.3 mm thick, 36 mm in",
                " diam.), sintered into oxide to fix to the plate.",
                "The number of atoms was detemrined by low geometry",
                " alpha-spectrometry and impurities were analyzed by",
                " mass spectrometry."
              ]
            }
          ],
